title: The Harry Potter Collection - J K Rowling
description:
Audio Books : Sci-Fi : Other quality : English


All Books in Series as both Ebooks and Audiobooks

Ebooks are in Epub format, cleaned and have covers and metadata and are calibre ready
Audiobooks are zipped and the .zip renamed to .zab (for Zipped Audio Book)
((Many Library managers assume a zip is an ebook archive))
just rename the .zab back to .zip and unzip it.



Enjoy and Seed!!
